This can make problems with windows mail app (if need that, leave this here)

Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\OneDrive
and change the DWORD string
PreventNetworkTrafficPreUserSignIn
to
1

&

Go to
HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\OneDrive
and change the DWORD string
DisablePersonalSync
to
1

&

Go to
HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Classes\CLSID\{018D5C66-4533-4307-9B53-224DE2ED1FE6}
and change the DWORD string
System.IsPinnedToNameSpaceTree
to
0


Finish. restart required.
